<h1>Ranger Spells</h1>

<h3 id=3D"firstLevelRangerSpells">1st-Level <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.o=
rg/srd/classes/ranger.htm">Ranger</a> Spells</h3>
<ul>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/a=
larm.htm">Alarm</a>:</strong> Wards an area for 2 hours/level.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/a=
nimalMessenger.htm">Animal Messenger</a>:</strong> Sends a Tiny animal to a=
 specific place.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/c=
almAnimals.htm">Calm Animals</a>:</strong> Calms (2d4 + level) HD of animal=
s.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/c=
harmAnimal.htm">Charm Animal</a>:</strong> Makes one animal your friend.</l=
i>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/d=
elayPoison.htm">Delay Poison</a>:</strong> Stops <a href=3D"https://www.d20=
srd.org/srd/specialAbilities.htm#poison">poison</a> from harming subject fo=
r 1 hour/level.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/d=
etectAnimalsOrPlants.htm">Detect Animals or Plants</a>:</strong> Detects ki=
nds of animals or plants.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/d=
etectPoison.htm">Detect Poison</a>:</strong> Detects <a href=3D"https://www=
.d20srd.org/srd/specialAbilities.htm#poison">poison</a> in one creature or =
object.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/d=
etectSnaresAndPits.htm">Detect Snares and Pits</a>:</strong> Reveals natura=
l or primitive traps.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/e=
ndureElements.htm">Endure Elements</a>:</strong> Exist comfortably in hot o=
r cold environments.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/e=
ntangle.htm">Entangle</a>:</strong> Plants <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.or=
g/srd/conditionSummary.htm#entangled">entangle</a> everyone in 40-ft.-radiu=
s circle.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/h=
ideFromAnimals.htm">Hide from Animals</a>:</strong> Animals can=E2=80=99t p=
erceive one subject/level.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/j=
ump.htm">Jump</a>:</strong> Subject gets bonus on <a href=3D"https://www.d2=
0srd.org/srd/skills/jump.htm">Jump</a> checks.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/l=
ongstrider.htm">Longstrider</a>:</strong> Increases your speed.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/m=
agicFang.htm">Magic Fang</a>:</strong> One <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.or=
g/srd/specialAbilities.htm#naturalWeapons">natural weapon</a> of subject cr=
eature gets +1 on attack and damage rolls.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/p=
assWithoutTrace.htm">Pass without Trace</a>:</strong> One subject/level lea=
ves no tracks.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/r=
eadMagic.htm">Read Magic</a>:</strong> Read scrolls and spellbooks.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/r=
esistEnergy.htm">Resist Energy</a>:</strong> Ignores 10 (or more) points of=
 damage/attack from specified energy type.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/s=
peakWithAnimals.htm">Speak with Animals</a>:</strong> You can communicate w=
ith animals.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/s=
ummonNaturesAllyI.htm">Summon Nature=E2=80=99s Ally I</a>:</strong> Calls a=
nimal to fight for you.</li>
</ul>

<h3 id=3D"secondLevelRangerSpells">2nd-Level <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.=
org/srd/classes/ranger.htm">Ranger</a> Spells</h3>
<ul>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/b=
arkskin.htm">Barkskin</a>:</strong> Grants +2 (or higher) enhancement to na=
tural armor.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/b=
earsEndurance.htm">Bear=E2=80=99s Endurance</a>:</strong> Subject gains +4 =
to Con for 1 min./level.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/c=
atsGrace.htm">Cat=E2=80=99s Grace</a>:</strong> Subject gains +4 to Dex for=
 1 min./level.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/c=
ureLightWounds.htm">Cure Light Wounds</a>:</strong> Cures 1d8 damage +1/lev=
el (max +5).</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/h=
oldAnimal.htm">Hold Animal</a>:</strong> Paralyzes one animal for 1 round/l=
evel.</li>
	<li><strong><a class=3D"spell" href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/spells/o=
wlsWisdom.htm">Owl=E2=80=99s Wisdom</a>:</strong> Subject gains +4 to Wis f=
or 1 min./level.</li>
